**Fazztrack - T-Shirt Printing Management System**

**Developed by:** Faiz Nasir  
**Company:** FazzPrint Sdn Bhd  
**Version:** 1.0.0  
**Release Date:** December 2024

**Contact Information:**
- **Email:** support@fazzprint.com
- **Website:** https://fazzprint.com
- **Phone:** +60 12-345 6789

**Technical Stack:**
- Laravel 10.x (PHP 8.2+)
- MySQL 8.0
- Docker & Docker Compose
- Tailwind CSS
- Alpine.js
- Font Awesome 6.4.0

**Features:**
- Complete order management workflow
- Role-based access control (SuperAdmin, Admin, Sales Manager, Designer, Production Staff)
- QR code tracking system
- Offline support for production staff
- Real-time analytics and reporting
- Design management with approval workflow
- Mobile responsive interface
- Time tracking and duration calculation

